 "remarks": "Offers due Friday 6/12/26 by 8 PM. This home is in a Great Location. This 3 bedroom, 1.5 bath home with den and oversized 3 car garage is located in the sought after Cranbury Area! The home is all on one level for your ease and convenience!! The living room/dining room combo is light and bright and has a picture window. The kitchen is eat in with a garden window. Main Bedroom has its own 1/2 bath. There are 2 Additional Bedrooms, one with a door to the 4 season family room with wood burning stove and sliders out to the deck. The home has a full fenced in back yard and 2 sheds for extra storage. There is an updated Full Bath and laminate floors throughout the home. This home has great value and worth some of the updates needed. This home is surrounded by more expensive homes and updating it will be well worth your time. Close to highways, dining, shopping and trains. Less than an hour from NYC.",
